description:
Levi (a.k.a. Leviathan) graduated from the University of Missouri, Columbia with a Bachelor of Fine Arts emphasizing in drawing and illustration in May 2010.

Since then, you may have seen his work in a number of Shadowrunsourcebooks, Halo: Evolutions Volume I, or the webcomic, A Fistful of Arrows. His next current project, Mayflower, an ongoing original series, can be read at MayflowerComic.com.
name: Levi Hoffmeier
